Text:
How does someone watch a 2 minute downloaded porn video  from brazzers website when it is in real player? I have my psp plugged in to the computer i open real player and drag the downloaded porn video to psp and it doesn't work. If you could help that would be awesome.

By the way thanks for uploading the Hung series.

The PSP doesn't read rmvb files. You need to convert them to mp4. Use XviD4PSP, PSPVC or PSP Video 9. I use XviD4PSP.

PS: The series wasn't that bad... Hope they'll do a second season.
